Package: bivnegbincp
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Change Point Detection for Bivariate Negative Binomial Sequences
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("A.", "Sinha", role = "aut"),
    person("J.", "Chen", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jiechen@augusta.edu")
  )
Description: Bayesian single and multiple change point detection for bivariate
    count sequences modeled using bivariate negative binomial distributions.
    The package provides constant-prior and Dirichlet-prior single change point
    posterior calculations, binary segmentation for multiple change point
    detection, and interactive visualization utilities.
